        <mxCell id="xKvwOOf8NLTHsFuvRd4J-30" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;u&gt;Sequence Diagram: Secure Video Playback Initiation&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="30" width="475" x="188" y="30" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="xKvwOOf8NLTHsFuvRd4J-31" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;u&gt;Description: Secure Video Playback Initiation&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;This diagram models the dynamic interaction required to start a secure video stream, incorporating conditional authentication logic.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;b&gt;Initiation:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/u&gt; The process begins with the Subscriber selecting a movie, triggering a GET request from the Web/Mobile App to the API Gateway.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;u&gt;Validation (ALT Frame):&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/b&gt; The API Gateway acts as a traffic controller, delegating session validation to the Auth Manager.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;u&gt;Success Path [token is valid]:&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/b&gt; The Streaming Manager generates a secure, time-limited key and returns a signed URL. The Web App then uses this link to pull high-bandwidth video data directly from the CDN, bypassing core services to optimize performance.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;u&gt;Failure Path [else]:&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/b&gt; If the session is invalid, the API Gateway immediately terminates the request and returns a 403 Forbidden error to the Web App, ensuring content security.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="30" width="610" x="168" y="760" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="xKvwOOf8NLTHsFuvRd4J-33" parent="1" style="verticalLabelPosition=bottom;verticalAlign=top;html=1;shape=mxgraph.basic.frame;dx=10;whiteSpace=wrap;" value="" vertex="1">
